AND HE ALSO SUGGESTS THAT IT

13:43.256 --> 13:44.957
COULD HELP CHILDREN WITH

13:44.957 --> 13:46.325
LEARNING DISABILITIES, AND THOSE

13:46.325 --> 13:47.593
FOR WHOM ENGLISH IS A SECOND

13:47.593 --> 13:48.961
LANGUAGE.

