SO I THINK YOU NEED THE LOOK AT

14:34.340 --> 14:35.975
THE WHOLE CHILD AND THE IMPACT

14:35.975 --> 14:37.009
THAT YEAR-ROUND EDUCATION CAN

14:37.009 --> 14:38.344
HAVE ON THE WHOLE CHILD, AND NOT

14:38.344 --> 14:39.112
JUST DOES IT MAKE YOUR TEST

