MARY C. SNOW WEST SIDE

14:45.485 --> 14:46.319
ELEMENTARY SCHOOL, ACROSS TOWN

14:46.319 --> 14:47.920
FROM PIEDMONT.

14:47.920 --> 14:49.122
THERE, ADMINISTRATORS ARE

14:49.122 --> 14:50.890
EXPERIMENTING WITH TWO WEEK

14:50.890 --> 14:52.325
INTERSESSIONS AND MAKING THE

14:52.325 --> 14:53.860
EXTRA TIME MANDATORY.

14:53.860 --> 14:55.228
AND AROUND THE STATE, YEAR-ROUND

14:55.228 --> 14:56.596
SCHOOLS HAVE RECENTLY BECOME A

14:56.596 --> 14:59.565
TOPIC OF DISCUSSION.

